# Raw character-art source dump (rork.com "Save Page As" export, ~86MB). The 9 chosen
# A-pose sprites were extracted + downscaled into assets/img/hero-*.png; the raw export
# is source material, not shipped — keep it out of git history.
assets/img/Brawl Arena Revamp.html
assets/img/Brawl Arena Revamp_files/

# Meshy intermediates — not shipped in-game (MODEL_FILES loads only the *-walk.glb + dennis.glb).
# The raw pre-remesh textured meshes (emily.glb/bo.glb ~15-18MB) and review PNGs are regenerable
# from the manifest task_ids, so keep them out of git history.
assets/meshy/emily.glb
assets/meshy/bo.glb
assets/meshy/*-tex.png
assets/meshy/*_base_color.png
